race.comment: They'll go like the clappers in this. ALTERMATUM (16) is a very honest commodity who is yet to miss the top-five in 14 career starts. Has only missed a drum once in six starts over this six-furlong journey and is nicely placed to give this a mighty shake. HELL (1) will strip fitter third-up from the break and gets some well-needed weight relief with the 3kg claim. Ready to find his best now. The well-related AMUSEANTES (12) (half to G1 winner Startantes) returned in fine fashion with a solid Doomben win and is one from one over this course and distance. Right in this contest. MEAN APPROACH (9) grows a leg for hoop Tilley who has four wins and a placing from just five rides. Include from the favourable draw.
